
  <sn><md>#### Phoenician Civilization

:::.row
:::.col-12 .col-md-6
The Phoenician civilization developed on a narrow strip of land located between the `Lebanon Mountains` and the `Mediterranean Sea`. The region did not have fertile land suitable for agriculture. As a result, their main source of income was `trade and commerce`.

:::
:::.col-12 .col-md-6
![Img](https://preview.redd.it/map-of-the-phoenician-civilization-in-331-bc-a-year-after-v0-7wxvyx9ll7u41.jpg?width=640\&amp;crop=smart\&amp;auto=webp\&amp;s=c67dbd8673e34f07308e2007daa9cecf5fd83de6)
:::
:::

```id="m9c4re"
Phoenician Civilization
        |
        +--&gt; Location
        |       |
        |       +--&gt; Lebanon Mountains
        |       +--&gt; Mediterranean Sea
        |
        +--&gt; Economy
                |
                +--&gt; Trade and Commerce
```
